            "single_product_tab_9QWQzR": {
              "type": "single-product-tab",
              "name": "Single product tabs",
              "settings": {
                "product_product_tab_margin": "0px 0px 0px 0px",
                "tab_title": "Shipping & Returns",
                "product_tab_selector": "custom",
                "tab_content": "<p><strong>Delivery</strong><br/><br/>We currently deliver within the UK only.<br/><br/>Orders are processed within 1–3 business days. Standard UK delivery usually takes 7–10 working days after dispatch.<br/><br/>Standard UK delivery is £4.99, or free on orders over £59.<br/><br/><strong>Returns</strong><br/><br/>We hope you love your Solisita piece. If it is not quite right, you may return eligible items within 14 days of receiving your order.<br/><br/>Items must be unworn, unused and returned in their original packaging. UK returns are free for eligible items.<br/><br/>For hygiene reasons, earrings cannot be returned unless faulty. Personalised or custom-made items are also non-returnable unless faulty.<br/><br/><strong>Warranty</strong><br/><br/>Solisita jewellery comes with a 1-year warranty covering manufacturing faults. This does not cover general wear and tear, accidental damage or damage caused by improper care.</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "single_product_tab_TecYTW": {
              "type": "single-product-tab",
              "name": "Single product tabs",
              "settings": {
                "product_product_tab_margin": "0px 0px 0px 0px",
                "tab_title": "Materials & Care",
                "product_tab_selector": "custom",
                "tab_content": "<p><strong>Materials</strong><br/><br/>Our jewellery is mainly crafted from durable stainless steel, designed for everyday styling with a polished, easy-to-wear finish.<br/><br/>Some pieces feature stones, crystals, pearls or decorative details. Please check each product’s details for specific material information.<br/><br/><strong>Care<br/></strong><br/>Many Solisita pieces are designed to be water-resistant and tarnish-resistant, making them suitable for everyday wear. To keep your jewellery looking its best, we recommend gently drying it after contact with water and storing it separately when not in use.<br/><br/>Avoid direct contact with perfume, lotions and harsh chemicals where possible.<br/><br/><strong>Packaging</strong><br/><br/>Each order is packed in a complimentary gift box or jewellery pouch, ready to treat yourself or someone special.</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
